248
00:12:28,645 --> 00:12:29,245
No need.

249
00:12:29,804 --> 00:12:30,964
She's not mad.

250
00:12:33,005 --> 00:12:34,285
We cherish each other

251
00:12:34,765 --> 00:12:37,285
