for trivial issues like that.

252
00:12:42,964 --> 00:12:43,525
Mi Bai.

253
00:12:44,165 --> 00:12:45,844
After this business trip,

254
00:12:46,964 --> 00:12:47,885
there are things

255
00:12:49,324 --> 00:12:51,724
